t-align:center\" |2016\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |All American Corners\n|-\n|El Alonzo, the Second Greatest Showman\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Show\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |2018\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Showtime Theater in Orleans Place\n|-\n|Sideshow\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Show\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |2015\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |All American Corners\n|-\n|Demon Re-Ignited\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Attraction\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |2017\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Country Fair\n|-\n|}\n\n===Attraction history===\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible collapsed\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! !! Year !! Haunted Mazes & Attractions !! Scare Zones !! Shows <!--Refs-->\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| 1 || 2008\n| Carnevil<br />Werewolf Canyon<br />Club Blood<br />Camp Gonna'getcha<br />Slaughterhouse<br />Cornstalkers\n| Underworld Alley<br />Dead Man's Cove<br />Witch Doctor's Trail<br />The Gauntlet\n| Ed Alonzo's Psycho Circus of Magic and Mayhem<br />Dave Hill's Haunted Hypnotics<br />Comedysportz Improv\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| 2 || 2009\n| Toy Factory <br />Carnevil <br />Werewolf Canyon <br />Club Blood <br />Camp Gonna'getcha <br />Slaughterhouse<br />Cornstalkers\n| Underworld Alley<br />Dead Man's Cove<br />Witch Doctor's Trail<br />The Gauntlet\n| Ed Alonzo's Psycho Circus of Magic and Mayhem<br />Dave Hill's Haunted Hypnotics<br />Shocking Sideshow of Freaks<br />SDC presents BANG!\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| 3 || 2010\n| Toy Factory<br />Carnevil<br />Werewolf Canyon<br />Club Blood<br />Black Widow's Cavern<br />Slaughterhouse<br />Cornstalkers\n| Underworld Alley<br />Dead Man's Cove<br />Witch Doctor's Trail<br />The Gauntlet\n| Fangs<br />Dave Hill's Haunted Hypnotics<br />Shocking Sideshow of Freaks<br />SDC presents BANG!\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| 4 || 2011\n| Toy Factory<br />Carnevil<br />Werewolf Canyon<br />Club Blood<br />Black Widow's Cavern<br />Slaughterhouse Annihilation<br />Cornstalkers\n| Underworld 